{"tid":1759470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB戰線進入最後直路 12/12前誓阻廣告商賣身俾TVB","createTime":"2019-11-27T16:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T18:27:30.000Z","uid":75759,"like":123,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"990f2d38210152ea2e0508fbd110576b05fd6454","tid":1759470,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"係呀！我冇打錯！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簽約=賣身俾TVB</span></strong>！點解咁講？試諗吓當你<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因爲TVB嘅過錯而慘被連累</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公司形象蒙受損失</span></strong>嘅時候，個仆街CCTVB講啲咩？佢諗埋啲屎橋教你hide comment掩耳盜鈴！Come on！Hide comment 、 block人呢啲我駛撚你教咩，你估真係個個好似你CCTVB啲撚樣咁戇鳩咩？問題係你CCTVB一日繼續做假新聞，我哋公司一日都要俾你拖累呀，而個重點係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>that is totally not my fault, but I have to pay the price！</strong></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Why should I be blamed for your fault？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n不過話CCTVB啲人戇鳩佢又唔戇鳩得曬，其實佢係好撚陰毒先真。第一，反正廣告費佢已經袋袋平安，佢理得你死呀！你公司蒙受損失？關我撚事咩又唔係我跌錢，who fucking cares？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你黎我度落得廣告就預咗有呢啲風險啦。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xrp9gfQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxrp9gfQ.jpg&h=a4833076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，佢鬼唔望你啲公司摺多兩間呀，最好全線摺埋全港攬炒𠻹！唔係佢邊有嘢抹黑啲所謂暴徒呀。衰啲講句，人哋大大條維穩水喉射住，你執咗佢搵其他紅色水源開單囉，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而你全公司上下乞食只會換到CCTVB2分鐘嘅airtime全力屌鳩啲暴徒，隨時搵埋唔陷尾上黎關心吓你、問吓你全公司陷家剷有咩感受呀、係咪宜得班暴徒死呀？</span></strong>以CCTVB嘅德性，你覺得佢做唔出？你自己諗吓呢一刻邊個最想你啲公司收皮啦。仲有，你以為公司執咗件事就完？對唔住，唔該你執笠前找埋條廣告費尾數先，我代表黨多謝你。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6YW0ob3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6YW0ob3.jpg&h=b107dc9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g9ehqqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg9ehqqp.jpg&h=34a7b233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三，當俾你負負碌碌頂過咗唔洗收皮，你都依然只係袁志偉個飛機杯，成世做TVB嘅奴才。咩話你今年廣告費用唔曬？咁我俾你帶落下年囉，不過你要同我簽埋下年喎。下年都唔曬？咁咪下下年繼續囉。你以為cable cut唔撚到好慘？你以為供呼吸plan買龍床盤好痛苦？少年，你太年輕了。咁係因為你未試過簽TVB成世俾袁志偉食住嘅滋味。<br />\n<br />\n如果睇到呢度你都仲要落TVB廣告，咁我唯有講，我真係恭喜你呀！最好年年有今日啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W5Yh9MR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW5Yh9MR.png&h=974e2d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ve635j7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVe635j7.jpg&h=1ba8fb65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔落TVB了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係戇鳩仔"},{"pid":"457127f9467ca1d59df3c4b754b1d1ba2f118cbe","tid":1759470,"uid":75759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"【終極任務最後一擊】<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>12/12</strong></span>就係CCTVB同廣告商簽約嘅死線喇，如果簽咗約嘅話CCTVB下年就穩賺！所以抵制TVB團隊精選咗50間課金最多嘅廣告商俾大家係12/12前瘋狂combo洗版同send email，係2019年1-10月呢50間總共俾咗約$30億廣告費俾CCTVB！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下大家唔好白費我地團隊同埋網民之前嘅努力，做埋最後呢round任務啦好無？！ 死線前最後一擊！如果2020年仲見到落廣告就永久罷買！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是日精選廣告商: (3/50間) <br />\n1. 御藥堂 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/royalmedic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Froyalmedic%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=3673ed8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/royalmedic/</a><br />\n2. 維特健寧 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vitagreenhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvitagreenhk%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=5d487fa4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vitagreenhk/</a><br />\n3. 衍生行<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hinsang/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhinsang%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=0ab593f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hinsang/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>留言template：</strong></span>、歡迎創意修改<br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！美麗華旅遊無視網民訴求，故要求美麗華集團回應。本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時抵制恆基集團旗下品牌。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n圖片link：<a href=\"http://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=1342150b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png</a><br />\n<br />\nEmail更有效用!<br />\nonline@vitagreen.com<br />\ninfo@wisdomcome.com<br />\ninfo@hshcl.com<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Email 範本</strong></span><br />\n電郵Title：自由創作！<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一定要修改電郵title</strong></span>否則可能被當作垃圾郵件攔阻<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n懇請要求不與無綫電視簽訂廣告合約<br />\n本人誠懇請求 貴公司承諾：不簽訂TVB 2020年度廣告合約、不贊助TVB任何節目，並且不以TVB藝人代言。<br />\n本人明白 貴公司或已簽訂今年廣告合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故現時只是暫時抵制。(暫時抵制清單: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JSJaQK&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=37b1903f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2JSJaQK</a> )<br />\n但若果明年仍能夠於CCTVB見到 貴公司的廣告、贊助及藝人代言等，恐怕網民將會將 貴公司的負面新聞制作成文宣圖，並將 貴公司列入「永久抵制名單」，然後將文宣及名單廣泛傳播，讓香港人永遠罷買。(負面新聞文宣圖例子: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XiUdc2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XiUdc2&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=1e776b84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XiUdc2</a>)<br />\n本人相信 貴公司若改變宣傳計劃，將資源投放於其他宣傳渠道（如ViuTV、NowTV、YouTube等），效果必定更佳。<br />\n本人懇請各大廣告商答應以上訴求，以挽回 貴公司優質形象。<br />\n**你嘅名**<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一次過洗曬TOP50廣告商就Perfect池喇:<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JSJaQK&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=37b1903f\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK</a><br />\n<br />\n預告：過咗12/12我地專頁將會有大改變，未必瘋狂洗版架喇。"},{"pid":"13542626e0d199960798a3d6d897fe255bdc3ecb","tid":1759470,"uid":101906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbf360f5419718e30df6c544c5bbf0413d6264ee","tid":1759470,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:10:28.000Z","msg":"CCTVB係極重要支線！係手足嘅唔該幫手推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c409986363982868aed48fecc49e55a3a42383da","tid":1759470,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:10:41.000Z","msg":"CCTVB係極重要支線！係手足嘅唔該幫手推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3e404c62b544ae2bca1eceab33f6e61866016f","tid":1759470,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:10:52.000Z","msg":"CCTVB係極重要支線！係手足嘅唔該幫手推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f435a8a63843293cc74b37ad8f57368dd175f7d3","tid":1759470,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd8e7bac97f65c3b42db5c38e99fb414468cd6a4","tid":1759470,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"tvb仆街垃圾"},{"pid":"b6d0194f5a9e4ea1d8383c940d921a9ba0e6a0cc","tid":1759470,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"becdb5cc5579656939bb696cf0ebb0f80ecf431e","tid":1759470,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:14:41.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"568239a5e7a59aeee3a4043275def48712d79e81","tid":1759470,"uid":241331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:15:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4c2f4aaaa9d5b9a87c06367426ef4384953c16d","tid":1759470,"uid":75759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"457127f9467ca1d59df3c4b754b1d1ba2f118cbe","tid":1759470,"uid":75759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"【終極任務最後一擊】<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>12/12</strong></span>就係CCTVB同廣告商簽約嘅死線喇，如果簽咗約嘅話CCTVB下年就穩賺！所以抵制TVB團隊精選咗50間課金最多嘅廣告商俾大家係12/12前瘋狂combo洗版同send email，係2019年1-10月呢50間總共俾咗約$30億廣告費俾CCTVB！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下大家唔好白費我地團隊同埋網民之前嘅努力，做埋最後呢round任務啦好無？！ 死線前最後一擊！如果2020年仲見到落廣告就永久罷買！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是日精選廣告商: (3/50間) <br />\n1. 御藥堂 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/royalmedic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Froyalmedic%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=3673ed8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/royalmedic/</a><br />\n2. 維特健寧 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vitagreenhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvitagreenhk%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=5d487fa4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vitagreenhk/</a><br />\n3. 衍生行<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hinsang/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhinsang%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=0ab593f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hinsang/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>留言template：</strong></span>、歡迎創意修改<br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！美麗華旅遊無視網民訴求，故要求美麗華集團回應。本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時抵制恆基集團旗下品牌。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n圖片link：<a href=\"http://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=1342150b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png</a><br />\n<br />\nEmail更有效用!<br />\nonline@vitagreen.com<br />\ninfo@wisdomcome.com<br />\ninfo@hshcl.com<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Email 範本</strong></span><br />\n電郵Title：自由創作！<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一定要修改電郵title</strong></span>否則可能被當作垃圾郵件攔阻<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n懇請要求不與無綫電視簽訂廣告合約<br />\n本人誠懇請求 貴公司承諾：不簽訂TVB 2020年度廣告合約、不贊助TVB任何節目，並且不以TVB藝人代言。<br />\n本人明白 貴公司或已簽訂今年廣告合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故現時只是暫時抵制。(暫時抵制清單: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JSJaQK&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=37b1903f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2JSJaQK</a> )<br />\n但若果明年仍能夠於CCTVB見到 貴公司的廣告、贊助及藝人代言等，恐怕網民將會將 貴公司的負面新聞制作成文宣圖，並將 貴公司列入「永久抵制名單」，然後將文宣及名單廣泛傳播，讓香港人永遠罷買。(負面新聞文宣圖例子: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XiUdc2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XiUdc2&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=1e776b84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XiUdc2</a>)<br />\n本人相信 貴公司若改變宣傳計劃，將資源投放於其他宣傳渠道（如ViuTV、NowTV、YouTube等），效果必定更佳。<br />\n本人懇請各大廣告商答應以上訴求，以挽回 貴公司優質形象。<br />\n**你嘅名**<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一次過洗曬TOP50廣告商就Perfect池喇:<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JSJaQK&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=37b1903f\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK</a><br />\n<br />\n預告：過咗12/12我地專頁將會有大改變，未必瘋狂洗版架喇。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"可附圖留言效果更佳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qxjtw8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxjtw8f.jpg&h=142bc1d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"681228d97eb6c0c8f331c229082661365e5b9fac","tid":1759470,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cl